<div class ="bodyMargin">
      <div class="featurette">
        <%=image_tag('tempmap.png', :class => "featurette-image pull-right")%>
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">Browse the map for bytes near you:</h2>
        <p class="paragraphStyle">Our easy to use map interface allows you to search anywhere on MIT's campus and alerts you to current bytes with dropped pins. You can click on a pin to view all offerings at that location, or if you're in a hurry, view all current offerings using our newsfeed. Just don't forget to click "all gone" if you took the last byte!</p>
      </div>

      <hr class="featurette-divider">
      <div class="featurette">
        <%=image_tag('food.png', :class => "featurette-image pull-left")%>
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">Leftover Food? Post a byte of your own</h2>
        <p class="paragraphStyle"> Create an account to post to our site and attract hungry MIT students to take those leftovers off your hands. We're also listening to MIT's free food mailing list, free-food@mit.edu, so send out an email and we'll take care of making it into a Byte!
        </p>
      </div>

      <hr class="featurette-divider">
      <div class="featurette  ">
        <%=image_tag('text.png', :class => "featurette-image pull-right")%>
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">Get Notified:</h2>
        <p class="paragraphStyle">Subscribe to the buildings you visit most often to receive text notifications when a new Byte has been posted. Never miss out on free food near you again! 
      </div>

      <hr class="featurette-divider">
      <div class="featurette">
        <%=image_tag('nofood.png', :class => "featurette-image pull-left")%>
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">Never Leave Disappointed</h2>
        <p class="paragraphStyle"> We clear out old Bytes periodically and leverage the Bytemap community to crowdsource Byte availability, so you'll never get to a Byte only to find that someon else took that last slice of pizza
        </p>
      </div>
